  "instructions": [
    "Bring vegetable broth to a boil in a large saucepan.",
    "Add brown rice noodles and cook according to package instructions.",
    "In a separate pan, heat vegetable oil over medium heat.",
    "Add garlic, ginger, and cilantro. Cook until fragrant.",
    "Stir in lime juice and season with salt and black pepper.",
    "Drain noodles and transfer to an ice bath to shock.",
    "Once chilled, add noodles to the pan with cilantro mixture and toss to combine.",
    "Serve immediately and garnish with additional cilantro if desired.",
    "Store leftover noodles in the refrigerator for up to 3 days.",
    "Reheat noodles in the pan over low heat to prevent overcooking."
